                <h2>Why Your Job Offer Is the Foundation of BC PNP</h2>
                <p>
                    For most <strong>BC PNP Skills Immigration streams</strong>, a valid job offer from a British Columbia employer is the single most important requirement. Without an eligible job offer, you cannot register in the BC PNP system, regardless of your education, language scores, or work experience.
                </p>
